'''''Tsotsi''''' ni  film yanditswe na tuyoborwa Gavin Hood na  Petero Fudakowski muri 2005 nibwo yasohotse<ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/tsotsi</ref>. ''Ni uguhuza'' igitabo cyitwa Tsotsi, cyanditswe na Athol Fugard Afurika yepfo / Ubwongereza bukorana<ref>https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/tsotsi-2006</ref>.  [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika y'Epfo]], hagaragaramo Presley Chweneyagae nka David / Tsotsi ( ''izina rya Tsotsitaal'' ryitwa "inkozi y'ibibi"), umusore wibye  imodoka gusa abona umwana yicaye inyuma<ref>https://www.developmenteducationreview.com/issue/issue-5/tsotsi</ref>. Irimo kandi Terry Pheto, Kenneth Nkosi, Jerry Mofokeng, na Rapulana Seiphemo<ref>https://www.commonsensemedia.org/movie-reviews/tsotsi</ref> . 

Amajwi y'iyi filime agaragaza umuziki wa Kwaito wakozwe n'umuhanzi wo muri Afurika y'Epfo Zola ndetse n'amanota ya Mark Kilian na Paul Hepker agaragaza ijwi ry'umuririmbyi wo muri Afurika y'Epfo wigaragambyaga akaba n'umusizi Vusi Mahlasela<ref>https://www.tvguide.com/movies/tsotsi/cast/2030050090/</ref> .

Iyi filime yakunzwe cyane, ishimwa cyane cyane iyandikwa, icyerekezo, ndetse n’imikorere<ref>https://theindependentcritic.com/tsotsi</ref>, cyane cyane ibya Chweneyagae na Pheto, sinema n’uburemere bw’amarangamutima<ref>http://www.miramax.com/movie/Tsotsi/</ref>. Yakomeje gutsindira igihembo cya Akademiki cya 2006 muri Filime nziza y’ururimi rw’amahanga kandi itorwa muri Golden Globe muri Filime Nziza y’indimi z’amahanga<ref>https://www.altfg.com/film/tsotsi/</ref>, iba filime ya mbere yo muri Afurika yepfo ndetse na filime ya mbere nyafurika idakozwe mu [[Igifaransa|gifaransa]] yatsindinze.    Muri 2009, yasubiwemo kumugaragaro muri [[Igitamili|Tamil]] nka ''Yogi'' <ref>https://www.definitions.net/definition/TSOTSI</ref>.<ref>https://www.bbfc.co.uk/education/case-studies/tsotsi</ref>

